You're eligible for a Genius discount at Aiello Hotels - Duomo! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.

Conveniently set in the center of Milan, Aiello Hotels - Duomo provides Italian breakfast and free WiFi. Featuring a bar, the hotel is close to several noted attractions, around a 2-minute walk from San Babila Station, half a mile from Montenapoleone Metro Station and a 6-minute walk from Galleria Vittorio Emanuele. Private parking can be arranged at an extra charge. The hotel will provide guests with air-conditioned rooms offering a desk, a coffee machine, a fridge, a safety deposit box, a flat-screen TV and a private bathroom with a bidet. Aiello Hotels - Duomo has certain units with city views, and every room comes with an electric tea pot. Popular points of interest near the accommodation include Duomo Square, Duomo Milan and Duomo Metro Station. The nearest airport is Milan Linate, 5 miles from Aiello Hotels - Duomo, and the property offers a paid airport shuttle service.

This is our guests' favorite part of Milan, according to independent reviews.

Aiello Hotels - Duomo has been welcoming Booking.com guests since Jun 6, 2022
